asset.author: Nike
asset.hookText: Go behind the scenes and see everything that went into the making of the new Nike SB commercial for the Eric Koston 2 shoe. Featuring Tiger Woods, Kyrie Irving, Neymar Jr., Allyson Felix, Danny Kass,Sean Malto, Wieger Van Wageningen, Ishod Wair, Alex Olson, Justin Brock, Neckface, Giovanni Reda, Jake Phelps, and more, this is an all-star event fit only for an amazing and beyond influential professional skater like Eric. Learn more about the Nike SB Eric Koston 2 at nikeskateboarding.com and explore Eric's unmatched career in amazing detail over at http://nikeskateboarding.com/thelegendgrows. #thelegendgrows #koston2
